CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 27, 1954, pg. 13 reads: "The Glamorous Cotillion - Scenes from the third annual debutante Cotillion given by Pittsburgh AKAs...center photos show part of the smartly gowned patrons who watched avidly as the beautiful pageant unfolded..."
TitMainTitle: Group, including Mary Jane Page, Betty Fowler, and Ann Barnett seated in center rear, gathered in Syria Mosque for Alpha Kappa Alpha 1954 Cotillion
